341
00:30:03.971 --> 00:30:06.679
<i>Le berger Moldave,
car il est plus brave,</i>


342
00:30:06.929 --> 00:30:10.888
<i>Il a plus d'agneaux,
Encornés et beaux,</i>


343
00:30:11.263 --> 00:30:15.179
<i>Des chevaux superbes
